---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import logoImage from '../assets/images/logo.webp';
import dentalImage from '../assets/images/dental.webp';
---

<div class="pt-6">
  <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-6 text-black dark:text-white slide-up">Work Experience üíº</h2>
  <ul
    class="space-y-8 border shadow-sm rounded-lg border-border dark:border-darkborder p-6 card-bg fade-in mt-2"
    style="animation-delay: 250ms"
  >
    <li class="border-b border-border dark:border-darkborder pb-8">
      <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
        <img
          src="/21impact-logo.svg"
          alt="21 Impact Labs Logo"
          width="48"
          height="48"
          class="rounded-md border border-border dark:border-darkborder shadow-md object-contain size-12 bg-darkgrey dark:bg-darkgrey p-1"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">Tech Lead, Software Engineer (Full Stack)</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-lighttext dark:text-darktext">21 Impact Labs üá®üá≠</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-xs text-lighttext dark:text-darktext mt-2 flex items-center my-auto">
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          width="24"
          height="24"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          class="size-3 mr-2 my-auto dark:text-darktext"
          style=""
          ><path d="M8 2v4"></path><path d="M16 2v4"></path><rect
            width="18"
            height="18"
            x="3"
            y="4"
            rx="2"></rect><path d="M3 10h18"></path><path d="M8 14h.01"></path><path d="M12 14h.01"
          ></path><path d="M16 14h.01"></path><path d="M8 18h.01"></path><path d="M12 18h.01"
          ></path><path d="M16 18h.01"></path></svg
        >
        September 2025 - Present
      </p>
      <ul class="text-xs mt-2 text-black dark:text-white list-disc pl-4 space-y-1">
        <li>
          Tech lead for the xponetiq Premium web platform, owning end-to-end delivery across frontend, backend, and AWS operations.
        </li>
        <li>
          Led MVP execution under aggressive timelines, translating product requirements into technical plans, estimates, and sprint delivery routines.
        </li>
        <li>
          Implemented the full Brain Health Index experience: new API integration, assessment user flows, results experience, and reliability improvements.
        </li>
        <li>
          Delivered the coaching booking product across frontend and backend, including scheduling integration and user flows.
        </li>
        <li>
          Built and shipped core platform features including authentication and access control, subscription and billing flows, and member lifecycle communications.
        </li>
        <li>
          Owned production readiness and reliability: CI/CD pipelines, deployments, environment configuration, AWS access management, and monitoring.
        </li>
        <li>
          Partnered with Product and leadership to refine scope, prioritize work, and unblock delivery, while providing technical oversight for the external iOS team.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li class="border-b border-border dark:border-darkborder pb-8">
      <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
        <Image
          src={dentalImage}
          alt="Clinica Dental Barcelo"
          width={48}
          height={48}
          class="rounded-md border border-border dark:border-darkborder shadow-md object-cover size-12"
          loading="lazy"
          format="webp"
          quality={80}
          densities={[1, 2]}
          sizes="48px"
        />
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">Full Stack Developer & Digital Consultant</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-lighttext dark:text-darktext">Clinica Dental Barcelo üá™üá∏</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-xs text-lighttext dark:text-darktext mt-2 flex items-center my-auto">
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          width="24"
          height="24"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          class="size-3 mr-2 my-auto dark:text-darktext"
          style=""
          ><path d="M8 2v4"></path><path d="M16 2v4"></path><rect
            width="18"
            height="18"
            x="3"
            y="4"
            rx="2"></rect><path d="M3 10h18"></path><path d="M8 14h.01"></path><path d="M12 14h.01"
          ></path><path d="M16 14h.01"></path><path d="M8 18h.01"></path><path d="M12 18h.01"
          ></path><path d="M16 18h.01"></path></svg
        >
        May 2023 - January 2025
      </p>
      <ul class="text-xs mt-2 text-black dark:text-white list-disc pl-4 space-y-1">
        <li>
          Led the clinic's digital transformation: custom website, appointment system, and internal tools using Next.js, Node, Astro, and PostgreSQL.
        </li>
        <li>
          Designed and developed inventory and billing apps that optimized operations and increased profitability by 80%.
        </li>
        <li>
          Contributed to rebranding and digital strategy, doubling patient intake.
        </li>
        <li>
          Acted as technical lead, working closely with management and staff to integrate new systems.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li class="border-b border-border dark:border-darkborder pb-8">
      <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
        <Image
          src={logoImage}
          alt="Benjami Bono's Logo"
          width={48}
          height={48}
          class="rounded-md border border-border dark:border-darkborder shadow-md object-cover size-12"
          loading="lazy"
          format="webp"
          quality={80}
          densities={[1, 2]}
          sizes="48px"
        />
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-black dark:text-white">Full Stack Developer</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-lighttext dark:text-darktext">Freelancer üåç</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-xs text-lighttext dark:text-darktext mt-2 flex items-center my-auto">
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          width="24"
          height="24"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          class="size-3 mr-2 my-auto dark:text-darktext"
          style=""
          ><path d="M8 2v4"></path><path d="M16 2v4"></path><rect
            width="18"
            height="18"
            x="3"
            y="4"
            rx="2"></rect><path d="M3 10h18"></path><path d="M8 14h.01"></path><path d="M12 14h.01"
          ></path><path d="M16 14h.01"></path><path d="M8 18h.01"></path><path d="M12 18h.01"
          ></path><path d="M16 18h.01"></path></svg
        >
        2020 - 2025
      </p>
      <ul class="text-xs mt-2 text-black dark:text-white list-disc pl-4 space-y-1">
        <li>
          Built responsive webapps for clients: e-commerce platform, Michelin-starred chef, MMA gym,
          local businesses, and city council. Helping both start-ups and established companies.
        </li>
        <li>
          Developed full-stack solutions for an education academy and public transport website using React,
          Python, Next.js, PostgreSQL, API integrations.
        </li>
        <li>
          Created Recipe Master, an AI-powered app with real-time features, auth, and nutritional analysis.
        </li>
        <li>
          Followed Scrum / Kanban (Agile), collaborating with product teams, designers, and stakeholders.
        </li>
        <li>Led projects end-to-end wearing many hats: requirements, dev, testing, deployment.</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
  </ul>
</div>
